---
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
---

<BlogLayout title="Singles - Page 2">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Oasis Singles</h1>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Live Forever (1994)</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <img 
              src="http://oasisreunion.live/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Live-forever.jpg" 
              alt="Live Forever Single Cover"
              class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-md mb-4"
            />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Single Statistics</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Release Date: August 8, 1994</li>
              <li>UK Chart Position: #10</li>
              <li>Weeks on Chart: 16</li>
              <li>Sales: Over 225,000 copies (UK)</li>
              <li>Parent Album: Definitely Maybe</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">B-Sides</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Up in the Sky (Acoustic)</li>
              <li>Cloudburst</li>
              <li>Supersonic (Live)</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Recording Details</h3>
              <p>Recorded at Loco Studios, Wales in 1993. The song was written by Noel Gallagher and became one of the band's signature tracks.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Cigarettes & Alcohol (1994)</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <img 
              src="http://oasisreunion.live/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cigarettes-and-alcohol.jpg" 
              alt="Cigarettes & Alcohol Single Cover"
              class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-md mb-4"
            />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Single Statistics</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Release Date: October 10, 1994</li>
              <li>UK Chart Position: #7</li>
              <li>Weeks on Chart: 14</li>
              <li>Sales: Over 260,000 copies (UK)</li>
              <li>Parent Album: Definitely Maybe</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">B-Sides</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>I Am The Walrus (Live Glasgow Cathouse June '94)</li>
              <li>Listen Up</li>
              <li>Fade Away</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Chart Performance</h3>
              <p>The single became their first UK top 10 hit and established them as one of Britain's leading rock bands.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <div class="flex justify-between mt-8">
        <a href="/singles" class="inline-block bg-black text-white px-6 py-2 rounded hover:bg-gray-800">
          ← Previous Page
        </a>
        <a href="/singles/3" class="inline-block bg-black text-white px-6 py-2 rounded hover:bg-gray-800">
          Next Page →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
